data.description: Tiny Encryption Algorithm in Perl & JS
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
This is the same module as Crypt::Tea. Windows users experience
    problems with the closeness between Crypt::Tea and Abhijit
    Menon-Sen's Crypt::TEA, and this renaming will cure those problems.
    It refers to the ability of Crypt::Tea to ecnrypt and decrypt
    compatibly in Perl and JavaScript.
